{"tid":2175870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強颱風同超強颱風個名好中國feel","createTime":"2020-08-26T17:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T18:07:11.000Z","uid":140953,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"202f484ac7dca470afebba2a02b402e803fa2440","tid":2175870,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:27:39.000Z","msg":"當年新設依兩個等級係想同中國制度一樣<br />\n但明明本身香港已經有強烈熱帶風暴依級<br />\n點解唔跟返自己個套，將強颱風改叫強烈颱風<br />\n超強颱風改做超級颱風"},{"pid":"116069f5b276aa55d293d055b96a5daa23de79b5","tid":2175870,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:35:32.000Z","msg":"話時話我到今時今日都唔知颱風/颶風/熱帶風暴/熱帶氣旋呢幾樣野有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7fb54bbb21d05ed47a708bbf2734cf2451e309","tid":2175870,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:38:04.000Z","msg":"Google下好難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱帶氣旋之分類<br />\n<br />\n依照世界氣象組織之建議，熱帶氣旋是根據接近風暴中心之最高持續風力加以分類的。香港採用的分類定義以10分鐘平均風速為根據，分為以下六種：<br />\n熱帶氣旋類別&nbsp;接近風暴中心之10分鐘最高平均風力<br />\n熱帶低氣壓&nbsp;每小時41至62公里<br />\n熱帶風暴&nbsp;每小時63至87公里<br />\n強烈熱帶風暴&nbsp;每小時88至117公里<br />\n颱風&nbsp;每小時118至149公里<br />\n強颱風*&nbsp;每小時150至184公里<br />\n超強颱風*&nbsp;每小時185公里或以上<br />\n* 2009年新增等級<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hko.gov.hk/tc/informtc/class.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Finformtc%2Fclass.htm&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatpMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=85413f26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hko.gov.hk/tc/informtc/class.htm</a>"},{"pid":"25054319c40b94b8d39e1460969a2d99c5bcca2a","tid":2175870,"uid":3357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"116069f5b276aa55d293d055b96a5daa23de79b5","tid":2175870,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:35:32.000Z","msg"